original_sentence: sI-MaxPUSCH-Duration \\ If present, indicate the maximum PUSCH duration of UL-SCH resources that this sidelink logical channel is mapped to, when checking the SR trigger condition. Corresponds to "sI-MaxPUSCH-Duration" in TS 38.321 [3].
